The,IBM,Watson,Language,Translation,API,uses,statistical,machine,translation,techniques,to,provide,domain,specific,translations,They,currently,offer,three,domains,that,can,translate,between,a,total,of,seven,languages,The,Conversational,and,News,domains,can,provide,translations,between,English,and,Arabic,Brazilian,Portuguese,French,and,Spanish,The,Patent,domain,can,provide,translations,between,English,and,Brazilian,Portuguese,Chinese,Korean,and,Spanish